This is an excerpt from  Bentley Publishers e-News Update - June 11,
2002, that
I received today...thought I would share it with the group...

"For the vintage community, we are still planning to produce V262
(Volkswagen
Transporter Workshop Manual: 1950-1962). This manual will be reproduced
from
original factory workshop manuals and is expected to be available by
Sept.
1st. Page count is expected to be approximately 1200 pages and retail
price
will be $109.95."

